snippet.title: Supergirl | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Look out. #Supergirl lands in theaters June 26.

“Supergirl,” DC Studios’ newest feature film to hit the big screen, will be in theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures, starring Milly Alcock in the dual role of Supergirl/Kara Zor-El.  Craig Gillespie directs the film from a screenplay by Ana Nogueira.

When an unexpected and ruthless adversary strikes too close to home, Kara Zor-El, aka Supergirl, reluctantly joins forces with an unlikely companion on an epic, interstellar journey of vengeance and justice.

Alcock stars alongside Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, and Jason Momoa.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and James Gunn are producing the film, which is based on characters from DC, Supergirl based on characters created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.  The film is executive produced by Nigel Gostelow, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars P. Winther.  Behind the camera, Gillespie is joined by director of photography Rob Hardy, production designer Neil Lamont, editor Tatiana S. Riegel, costume designer Anna B. Sheppard, Visual Effects Supervisor Geoffrey Baumann, and composer Ramin Djawadi.  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment Production, The Safran Company Production, A Film by Craig Gillespie, “Supergirl,” which will be in theaters and IMAX® across North America on June 26, 2026, and internationally beginning 24 June 2026, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

#Jaani #BPraak #NewMusic 

Lyrics - 

Ek Toh Parvardigaar Ke Baare Mein Na Boliye
Aur Phir Aitbaar Ke Baare Mein Na Boliye
Aapka Hum Qatal Bhi Kar Sakte Hain
Aap Hamare Yaar Ke Baare Mein Na Boliye

Humse Woh Mila Hi Nahin Hai Sadiyon Se
Taras Gaye The Hum Yaar Ke Saath Ko
Us Bewafa Ka Dil Kaat Ke Dekhna Hai
Woh Kiske Liye Roya Tha Kal Raat Ko

Mera Dil Gaya Dil Gaya Dil Gaya Dil Gaya
Dil Gaya Dil Gaya Bewafa
Mainu Mil Gaya Mil Gaya Mil Gaya Mil Gaya
Mil Gaya Mil Gaya Bewafa

Mujhe Toh Rulaya Hi Hai
Mujhe Toh Hasaya Hi Nahin
Mujhme Kami Kya Thi
Yaar Ne Bataya Hi Nahin

Teri Hi Gali Se Mera Guzra Janaza Tha
Maine Awaaz Di Thi Tu Baahar Aaya Hi Nahin

Tere Kolon Choor Hoke Enni Majboor Hoke
Haukeyan Lag Gayi Aan Main
Paagal Banayi Payi Aan
Jama Hi Hilaayi Payi Aan
Nasheyan Te Lag Gayi Aan Main
Ho Jaani Hai Mera Dushman

Main Aisi Nazar Utaarungi
Tu Beech Mein Aa Na Duniya
Jaani Ko Main Hi Maarungi

Woh Gala Bhi Mera Kaate Toh Koi Baat Nahin
Main Kaat Nahin Sakti Uski Baat Ko

Us Bewafa Ka Dil Kaat Ke Dekhna Hai
Woh Kiske Liye Roya Tha Kal Raat Ko

Kitne Deewane Rakh Rakhe Hain God Mein
Ik Aane Lag Jaata Hai Ik Jaane Lag Jaata Hai
Aapke Pairon Se Kya Mohabbat Hai Duniya Ko
Jo Aata Hai Dabaane Lag Jaata Hai

Hai Soyi Thi Kabar Mein Woh Jag Gayi Kya Bolun
Mujhe Uski Aisi Aadat Lag Gayi Hai Kya Bolun

Main Jugnu Ko Bolun Sooraj
Aur Bande Ko Khuda Bolun
Mujhe Uski Aisi Aadat Lag Gayi Hai Kya Bolun

Mere Pairon Mein Jo Chubh Gaye
Woh Kaante Kaun Nikaalega
Oh Hai Koi Yahan Bola
Jo Ik Laash Ko Paa Lega

Woh Phir Bhi Hai Jaan Meri
Meri Pehchaan Rahega Woh
Jaan Woh Tha Jaan Hai Woh
Aage Bhi Jaan Rahega Woh

Maine Yaar Mere Ko Chhoda Tha Sava Saat Baje
Woh Kisi Aur Ka Ho Gaya Paune Aath Ko

Us Bewafa Ka Dil Kaat Ke Dekhna Hai
Woh Kiske Liye Roya Tha Kal Raat Ko

Yeh Aajkal Sabko Kya Ho Gaya Hai
Bure Logon Ki Ho Rahi Hai Umr Lambi
Achhe Log Mar Jaa Rahe Hain

Us Bewafa Ka Dil Kaat Ke Dekhna Hai

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, Avengers: Doomsday positions itself as the opening act of the Multiverse Saga’s final confrontation, where Victor von Doom rises as a master of science and sorcery who believes the multiverse must be controlled to be saved. As Earth’s heroes stand divided, Sam Wilson’s Captain America attempts to rebuild the Avengers while rival teams and uneasy alliances complicate any hope of unity. The arrival of the Fantastic Four from another reality and the long-awaited emergence of the X-Men signal that the conflict can no longer be contained within a single universe. With incursions threatening to collapse entire timelines, Doom’s ideology challenges heroes and gods alike, drawing figures like Loki into a battle over who truly holds the right to shape existence. The story frames Doomsday as a turning point where legacy, power, and sacrifice collide, setting the stage for a multiversal reckoning that will define the future of the Marvel universe.

snippet.title: KIS KISKO PYAAR KAROON 2: Official Trailer | Kapil Sharma, Manjot Singh |In Cinemas 12 December 2025
snippet.description:
Kapil Sharma is back with his clean comedy capers and how 🎬🤣 
Presenting the official trailer of 'Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon 2', starring Kapil Sharma, Manjot Singh, Hira Warina, Tridha Choudhary, Parul Gulati and others. This is a sequel to the blockbuster 'Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon', Kapil Sharma's debut film.  #KisKiskoPyaarKaroon2 #KapilSharma #ManjotSingh 

Experience this laugh riot with your entire family in cinemas on 12th December 2025 🤣🤣

'Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon 2' is presented by Star Studio18 & Venus Worldwide Entertainment in association with Abbas Mustan Films Production, is written & directed by Anukalp Goswami and is produced by Ratan Jain, Ganesh Jain & Abbas Mustan.

snippet.title: [URDU] 2025 PMGC Grand Finals | Day 3 | PUBG MOBILE Global Championship
snippet.description:
Aakhir wo din aachuka jiska sabko intezar tha, 2025 PUBG MOBILE GLOBAL CHAMPIONSHIP k Grand Finals k  teesry din mai khush aamdeed!

Yahi hai aakhri maidan-e-jang. Na koi doosri koshish na koi doosra mauqa.
Saal bhar ki mehnat, paseena aur khawab sirf in in aakhri lamhaat main apna rang dikhayenge.
Aaj raat, ek naya champion ubhar kar samne aayega. 👑🔥

Is saal ka format dobara badla gaya hai taa k shaiqeen aur waqar k peche bhagny wali teamain dono ko zyada lutf haasil ho.
Pehla bara twist "The Gauntlet Stage" tha.
Duniya ki 16 behtareen teamon ne yahan bary dao laga kr muqabla kia.
Dao Pech? Har mumkin lagaye gye.

Rank 1 ta 7: Seedha Grand Finals mein pohanch gyin.
Rank 8 ta 16: Group Stage se ek aur mauqa hasil kia.

Group Stage mai har group se upper ki 3 teamain seedha Grand Finals ke liye qualify kr gain.
Jo teamain 4th–11th par thin unko Last Chance khelny ka akhri mauqa mila.
Lekin jo 12th–16th par aayegi, unka 2025 PMGC ka safar wahin khatam ho gya.
Aakhir mein, Last Chance (Dec 6 ta 7) teamon k liye aakhri parao tha.

Ab jab k wo aakhri marhala aa chuka hai, jahan maidaan hai saja or shor hai barpaa.

To kyu na Khush aamdeed kia jae 2025 PUBG MOBILE GLOBAL CHAMPIONSHIP Mai — Jahan sarbulandi hasil krny k liye ek Faisla Kun Jung Hogi!

snippet.title: Anuv Jain - INAAM (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
The 15th studio recorded single - Inaam, written, sung and composed by #AnuvJain is here!

Listen to 'Inaam' on all streaming platforms : https://UMGI.lnk.to/Inaam_AnuvJain


Audio Credits: 

Artist: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Composer: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Producer: Lost Stories (@loststories)
Guitars: Keba Jeremiah (@kebajr)
Choirs: Solomon Konwar (@eskay______) Prachi Kapil (@prachi.kapil8)
Mix Engineers: Rishab Joshi (@rishabjoshi) & Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Master Engineer: Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Recording Engineer: Jay Rana (@itsjayrana)
Additional Programming: Sarthak Kalyani (@sarthak.kalyani)
Dolby Atmos Mastered at Ferris Wheel Studios (@ferriswheelstudios)

Video Credits: 

Director: Bhagyesh Rajeshirke (@bhagyesh_rajeshirke)
Associate Director: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Creative Director: Pranjal Asha (@pranjalasha)
Editor: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Producer: Arnab Kar (@arnab_kar)

Management: REPRESENT
Managers: Shirsodhi Banerjee (@shirsodhi), Kartik Iyer (@kartik_iyer_)

Inaam Lyrics: 

Paragraph 1

Malum 
Hai na 
Hum janay 
Tumko tumse zyada

Tumko 
Mila hai woh
Saalon se 
Jo bhi hai manga

Pre-chorus 1

Kaise khilono ki 
Ro ro ke
Karte the mangay 

Ik bar mil jaye 
Do din mein
Hi bhul jatay  

Chorus 1

Lekin khilono ke dil 
Toh hote hi nahin the

Dil toh humara hai 
Janay galat kya sahi yeh

Kitna the chahte par
Ab tumko yaad na aatey 
Hum

Paragraph 2

Kya yaad tumko 
Tum humko
‘Inaam’ the kehte 

Karte the kitna kuch
Panay ki chah 
Mein pehlay 


Pre-chorus 2

Ab yeh inaam ka 
Tum pe ilzaam hai jana

Dil hai gawah
Jeete jabse ho
Tumko hai hara 

Chorus 2

Cheezein badalti hain 
Itna toh hum ne bhi mana

Itna badal jaogay 
Jana kisne tha jana  

Jo tha parvana 
Ab usko humari parwah na 
Kyun?

Pre-Bridge

Dil mein baat kya hai?
Haan bolo humse 

Chahta aur kya hai? 
Haan bolo humse

Kya kami yahan hai?
Haan bolo humse na

Jo kaha mila hai
Haan bolo humse 

Badle mein bhala hai
Haan bolo humse

Manga tumse kya hai
Hai manga zara sa hi, kya hi, 

Kya? haye

Bas 

Bridge

Jo khat likhe the tumne 
Unhe padh bhi lo zara 
Waadein kiye the jo bhi
Nibhao na aise kabhi

In waadon ki siyahi 
Abhi sukhi hi kahan?
Hai tumhari hi likhai
Yaan bhule ho ye bhi?

Paragraph 3

Kehne ko 
Wah wah 
Tum phir se 
Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan 
Par ankhein hain
Khush na kahin se 

Pre-chorus 3

Humne kaha tha
Hum janey tumko 
Tumse zyada 

Shayad galat the 
Par itna toh 
Humne hai jana 

Chorus 3

Har woh inaam 
Qadar ke bina hi hai waise 

Ghar mein padhe, 
Dhul khate khilono ke jaise

Pal bhar behlaye 
Par dil ko yeh khush na kar paye 
Yoon

Hidden verse

Ghar bethe likhta tha 
Dil ki kahani meri 

Charon taraf thi deewarein 
Deewaron se hi 

Kehta tha ik din 
Jahaan hoga haathon mein hi

Aa aa

Jo tha gumnamo mein 
Ab woh inaamon pe bhi 

Qaidi hai, Qaid hi hai 
Phir bhi dewaron mein hi 

Namumkin khwabon mein
Na khush udane meri 

Aa aa
